flowchart TD
    A1[Paper / PDF]:::src --> B
    A2[Submitted thesis]:::src --> B
    A3[Code-complete strategy]:::src --> B
    A4[Generated hypothesis]:::src --> B

    B[Ingest and grounded extraction]:::proc --> C[Screen: relevance and falsifiability]:::proc
    C --> D[Economic preflight and dedup]:::proc
    D --> E{Route the claim}:::dec
    E -->|known class| F[Trusted module]:::proc
    E -->|novel| G[Reconstruct in Docker sandbox]:::proc
    F --> H[Point-in-time data assembly]:::proc
    G --> H
    H --> I[Backtest harness]:::proc
    I --> J["Robustness and power gates<br/>DSR · bootstrap · permutation<br/>regime · walk-forward · cost"]:::gates
    J --> K{Verdict}:::dec

    K --> KILL[kill]:::kill
    K --> UP[underpowered]:::under
    K --> W[watch]:::watch
    K --> RS[research-supported]:::rs

    RS -.->|confirm once| HO[(Locked holdout)]:::holdout
    HO -.-> RS

    KILL --> CORP[(Corpus of invalidations)]:::corpus
    UP --> CORP
    W --> CORP
    CORP -.->|prior on new claims| D

    RS --> AUTH[Human authorization]:::proc
    AUTH --> REP[Report and dashboard]:::proc

    USER([Researcher]):::user <--> PENNIE["Pennie<br/>chat research assistant"]:::pennie
    CORP -.->|discovery-safe grounding| PENNIE
    PENNIE -.->|drafts a falsifiable thesis, you confirm| A2

